        <section>
            <section.front>
                <doc.title toc-guid="I94cbf030e1e311da9c26e67ca3b71335">
                    <head parent="doc.title">
                        <bop/>
                        <bos/>
                        <label.name>§</label.name>
                        <label.designator>2:5.</label.designator>
                        <headtext>Functioning of the Panel</headtext>
                        <eos/>
                        <eop/>
                    </head>
                </doc.title>
            </section.front>
            <section.body>
                <para>
                    <bop/>
                    <bos/>
                    <paratext>The Panel has functioned well since its early days.
                        <eos/>
                        <bos/>The Panel&apos;s initial make-up of judges who had served on the Coordinating Committee
                        and who had handled complex, multidistrict cases helped it establish a smooth-running and
                        effective set of procedures.
                        <eos/>
                        <bos/>Although the Panel&apos;s rules have been changed over the years, the rules initially
                        adopted in <?page no="16"?> 1968 bear a striking resemblance to those now in effect.
                        <eos/>
                        <bos/>The procedures, like the VW Beetle, have been periodically updated, but the initial design
                        continues to serve well.[
                        <eos/>
                        <bos/>
                        <footnote.reference refid="I01fea4a0680911e88f4a9c1f64101294">1</footnote.reference>]
                    </paratext>
                    <eos/>
                    <eop/>
                </para>
                <para>
                    <bop/>
                    <bos/>
                    <paratext>The smooth running of the Panel does not mean that the decisional process has been simple
                        or automatic.
                        <eos/>
                        <bos/>In a few of the Panel&apos;s decisions over the years one or more Panel member has
                        dissented from the Panel majority&apos;s decision.[
                        <eos/>
                        <bos/>
                        <footnote.reference refid="I01fecbb1680911e88f4a9c1f64101294">2</footnote.reference>] Panel
                        members have also disagreed with portions of the decision of the Panel and have filed concurring
                        or concurring and dissenting opinions.[
                        <eos/>
                        <bos/>
                        <footnote.reference refid="I01ff19d0680911e88f4a9c1f64101294">3</footnote.reference>]
                    </paratext>
                    <eos/>
                    <eop/>
                </para>
            </section.body>
